      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARD QUESTIONS (4) improved last time out when beaten 1.5L at the mile here and steps out in distance again today. He boasts a good record at this track and trip and Riordan's claim comes in handy. Best form is brilliant for a race like this and he can get back to winning ways. BAYHARA (2) sat on the speed two back to win by 0.5L over 1931m at this track before tackling Saturday company at Ascot most recently where she wasn't disgraced. Back to this track and trip is a big tick for her and Faithfull sticks with her. Can bounce back to winning ways. BOMBAY STYLE (1) stuck on well over the 1600m journey here last time out and he boasts a good record over this track and trip placing in 2/4. He's performed well in this grade previously and he's sure to make his presence felt. ALTERNO (7) can improve out in trip today and with the aid of an inside barrier. TIGER LINE (12) is better than he showed last time out can bounce back.",
